direction: down

Mic: {label: "**Mic capture**\n16kHz mono PCM"}

STT: {label: "**Google STT**\nCloud Speech-to-Text v2\nstreaming_recognize"}

Partials: {label: "**Partial transcripts**\nprinted/updated"}

Final: {label: "**Final transcript**"}

DSPy: {label: "**DSPy**\ntransform text\n(Gemini LM)"}

TTS: {label: "**Google TTS**\n(Gemini Live audio-out OR Cloud TTS)"}

Play: {label: "**Playback**\nstream or play wav"}

Mic -> STT -> Partials -> Final -> DSPy -> TTS -> Play
